  <name>Speech Note</name>
  <summary>Note taking and reading with Speech to Text and Text to Speech</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Speech Note enables you to take and read notes with your voice.
      It uses Speech to Text and Text to Speech conversions to do so.
      All voice processing is entirely done off-line, locally on your
      computer without the use of network connection. Your privacy is
      always respected. No data is send to the Internet.</p>
  </description>
